         <t:div type="edition">
            <t:div type="textpart" subtype="incipit" xml:lang="gez">
               <t:ab>
                  ስምዑ፡ አኀዊነ፡ ንዜንወክሙ፡ ዜና፡ ሐዲዘ፡ ዜናሆሙ፡ ለብፁዓን፡ ቅዱሳን፡ ጻድቃን፡ ዘኮኑ፡ በመዋዕለ፡ ኤርምያስ፡ ነቢይ፡  
                  <t:gap reason="omitted"/> ወነግሠ፡ ፩ንጉሥ፡ ዘስሙ፡ ሴዴቅያስ፡
               </t:ab>
            </t:div>
            <t:div type="textpart" subtype="explicit" xml:lang="gez">
               <t:ab>
                  ወአንበረ፡ ውስተ፡ ቤተ፡ ክርስቲያን፡ ዮሐንስ፡ መጥምቅ። ስብሐት፡ ለአብ፡ <t:gap reason="omitted"/> ዘከሠተ፡ ሎሙ፡ ምሥጢራተ፡ 
                  <t:gap reason="omitted"/> እምርስሐተ፡ ዝንቱ፡ ዓለም፡ ኀላፊ፡ በምሕረተ፡ <t:gap reason="omitted"/>
               </t:ab>
            </t:div>
            <t:note>The following division into textparts is based on <t:bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/BNJJJBEU"><seg type="bookSection"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Brankaer2016VersionEthiopienne"/><title level="a">La tradition éthiopienne</title><title level="m">Histoire de Zosime sur la vie des Bienheureux Réchabites: Les versions orientales et leurs manuscrits</title><title level="s">Corpus Scriptorum Christianorum Orientalium</title><author><forename>Johanna</forename><surname>Brankaer</surname></author><editor><forename>Jean-Claude</forename><surname>Haelewyck</surname></editor><pubPlace>Lovanii</pubPlace><publisher>In aedibus Peeters</publisher><date>2016</date><series><title level="s">Corpus Scriptorum Christianorum Orientalium</title><biblScope unit="volume">664, Subsidia, 135</biblScope></series><biblScope unit="page">93-98</biblScope><biblScope unit="volume">664, Subsidia, 135</biblScope><note type="tags"><note type="tag">bm:Brankaer2016VersionEthiopienne</note></note><note type="tag">bm:Brankaer2016VersionEthiopienne</note></t:bibl>.</t:note>
